title: Cartoon Explosion Elements
longDescription:
Enjoy the dynamic and action animation template, which includes a unique collection of Cartoon Explosion elements!

This package contains 10 Cartoon Explosion sprite sheet animations for 2D Games.

         

Features:

● Sprite animations work much better than any other shaders and particles due to

memory capacity.

● Optimized for games.

● Pivot point set properly.

● No setup or plug-ins required.

● All materials, sprites and other parts of pack properly named.
